&lt;p&gt;Salaried GP&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Sidings Medical Practice, Sleaford Road, Boston&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Lincolnshire Community Health Service is currently seeking GP’s to join our Community Trust. These roles sit within our primary care portfolio which covers our GP practices services. These posts are for salaried GPs to support the Clinical Lead GP, based at The Sidings practice Boston.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The surgery is located on Sleaford Road in Boston and is purpose built to provide the highest quality primary health care to patients and their families in the area.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are entering a period of growth, the list size is increasing every week and as a result we seek experienced GPs who wish to work within an established primary care service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;LCHS is looking for experienced and adaptable GPs to become part of a friendly, innovative and ambitious practice team, dedicated to supporting patients to manage their own health and reducing the need for unnecessary hospital visits and admissions&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are rated ‘Outstanding&#39; by the Care Quality Commission and aim to maintain this rating this year and beyond. We play an integral part in shaping future health service provision countywide alongside partner health and social care organisations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
